    "description": "创立一个时代，在这个时代里电不是一种固有的东西，而是伟大发明家的想象力，在lit的世界里，你可以听从自己的内心的工程师，让你发现用光进行直接实验的乐趣。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190160/extras/17d77e0dacb33ac0f8501a841b2d6ccf.poster.avif?t=1695457269\" width=736 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190160/extras/17d77e0dacb33ac0f8501a841b2d6ccf.webm?t=1695457269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190160/extras/17d77e0dacb33ac0f8501a841b2d6ccf.mp4?t=1695457269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190160/extras/ee6c0ec75c64ba8d2ca65f786464694b.webp?t=1695457269\" width=633 height=50 /></span><br>在LIT世界里，灯的每步操作都被设计得精准无比。你可以理解为在LIT世界里设计出来的灯的路径很可能在现实中展现。仅仅需要按几下鼠标，你便可以自由地设计镜子和玻璃来折射和反射光线<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190160/extras/8c0b69aa11814699e18604b3a26f43a9.webp?t=1695457269\" width=633 height=50 /></span><br>我们的游戏是开放式结局。我们只会提供给你基本的规则和所需要的的工具，期待你给我们展示如何解决它。我们在每个关卡设计了许多可能的解法并且让你尽情发挥才能---我们只希望‘你以为’，而不是‘我们以为’。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190160/extras/91f7f913959a5aba37f1c260c6c3c8e4.webp?t=1695457269\" width=633 height=50 /></span><br>在卡通和现实之间的细线上穿插视觉效果。节奏很好。放松的音乐，让你进入。所有这些创造了一个独特的，神秘但温暖的气氛。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190160/extras/cb5e402ec5a9e29820a8a30abaa659fa.poster.avif?t=1695457269\" width=736 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190160/extras/cb5e402ec5a9e29820a8a30abaa659fa.webm?t=1695457269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190160/extras/cb5e402ec5a9e29820a8a30abaa659fa.mp4?t=1695457269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190160/extras/5d7796dbe53c478c3a54eae9d7c2bec9.webp?t=1695457269\" width=633 height=50 /></span><br>当灯光照射到镜子会发生反射，当灯光照到玻璃会发生反射。这就是全部。当然与此同时会产生成千上万的可能性，这就意味着我们的每一关都是独一无二的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190160/extras/7997c57441d6534a9f99cefd1b84c51b.webp?t=1695457269\" width=633 height=50 /></span><br>LIT简洁易懂。通过多个游戏测试证明了它人人皆宜。你想找出不同的方法来进一步探险吗？想找一款适合五岁孩子的游戏吗？亦或是试图让你的母亲体验游戏的乐趣？仅需要一个手柄或者鼠标，LIT能够满足你的全部。",
